When you hear “I’m a savage, classy, bougie, ratchet…”, you think of how Megan Thee Stallion’s hit has gradually become the anthem of people who believe they can be all of the above. What’s more, is it has been sprinkled with a bit of the “Queen Bee” spice. That’s right! Beyoncé has hopped on the official remix of Megan Thee Stallion’s viral sensation “Savage”. On Wednesday, a surprise remix to the viral hit was released featuring none other than Queen Bey. The bossy hit features a classy and ratchet Beyonce repping “gang gang gang” and rapping about everything from TikTok to her behind. Listen to Savage remix below: 